-*- mode:org -*-
* Requirements:
** lua 5.1, 5.2, 5.3 ( http://www.lua.org/ ) or LuaJIT 2.x ( http://www.luajit.org/ )
** Apache HTTPD 2.4 ( http://httpd.apache.org/ ) or higher

* Documentation
  See docs/README

* Building
  For now, see docs/building-from-subversion.txt


